	<p><anchor n="T.50.2059.0373a16"/><lb ed="T" n="0373a16"/><persName key="A002244">釋曇斌</persName>，姓蘇，<placeName key="CN0411302Z03AA">南陽</placeName>人。十歲出家，事<persName key="A002984">道禕</persName>為<lb ed="T" n="0373a17"/>師。始住<placeName key="CN0422422T01AA">江陵<ptr target="fn04"/>新寺</placeName>，聽經論，學禪道，覃思<lb ed="T" n="0373a18"/>深至，而情未盡達。夜夢神人謂<persName key="A002244">斌</persName>曰：「汝所<lb ed="T" n="0373a19"/>疑義，遊方自決。」於是振錫挾衣，殊邦問道。<lb ed="T" n="0373a20"/>初下<placeName key="CN0320106Z06AA">京師</placeName>，仍往<placeName key="CN0320503Z22AA">吳郡</placeName>。值<persName key="A002318">僧業</persName>講《十誦》，飡聽<lb ed="T" n="0373a21"/>少時，悟解深入。後還<placeName key="CN0320106Z06AA">都</placeName>，從<persName key="A002970">靜林法師</persName>諮受<lb ed="T" n="0373a22"/>《涅槃》，又就<placeName key="CN0330521T01AA">吳興小山</placeName><persName key="A002250">法<ptr target="fn05"/>珍</persName>研訪《泥洹》、《勝鬘》，<lb ed="T" n="0373a23"/>晚從<placeName key="CN0320101T54AA">南林</placeName><persName key="A002589">法業</persName>，受《華嚴》、《雜心》。既遍歷眾師，<lb ed="T" n="0373a24"/>備聞異釋，迺潛思積時，以窮其妙。融冶百<lb ed="T" n="0373a25"/>家，陶貫諸部。於是還止<placeName key="CN0610116A01AA">樊</placeName>、<placeName key="CN0610727Z29AA">鄧</placeName>，開筵講說，四<lb ed="T" n="0373a26"/>遠名賓，負[袌-包+矢]皆至。</p><p>及<date key="j18869261888017" notAfter-iso="0457" notBefore-iso="0454">孝建</date>之初，勅<persName key="A002647">王玄謨</persName><lb ed="T" n="0373a27"/>資發出京。初止<placeName key="CN0320101T59AA">新安寺</placeName>，講《小品》、《十地》，并申<lb ed="T" n="0373a28"/>頓悟漸悟之旨。時心競之徒，苦相讎校，<persName key="A002244">斌</persName>既<lb ed="T" n="0373a29"/>辭愜理詣，終莫能屈。<placeName key="CN0411626Z27AA">陳郡</placeName><persName key="A002985">袁粲</persName>，令望當時，而<lb ed="T" n="0373b01"/>嘉<persName key="A002244">斌</persName>行解，嘗令中書舍人<persName key="A002986">巢尚介</persName>意欲試<lb ed="T" n="0373b02"/><persName key="A002244">之</persName>，<persName key="A002244">斌</persName>不為屈，<persName key="A002985">粲</persName>迺躬自往候。粲每勸<persName key="A002244">斌</persName>數<lb ed="T" n="0373b03"/>覲<persName key="A002105">天子</persName>，<persName key="A002244">斌</persName>曰：「<persName key="A002244">貧道</persName>方外之人，豈宜與<persName key="A002105">天子</persName><lb ed="T" n="0373b04"/>同<ptr target="fn06"/>趣。」<persName key="A002985">粲</persName>益以高之，後請為母師。<persName key="A002987">宋建平王<lb ed="T" n="0373b05"/>景素</persName>亦諮其戒範。<date key="j18938651895488" notAfter-iso="0477" notBefore-iso="0473">宋元徽中</date>，卒於<placeName key="CN0320101T60AA">莊嚴寺</placeName>，春<lb ed="T" n="0373b06"/>秋六十有七。</p><p>時<placeName key="CN0320101T60AA">莊嚴</placeName>復有<persName key="A002988">曇濟</persName>、<persName key="A002989">曇宗</persName>，並以學<lb ed="T" n="0373b07"/>業才力見重一時。<persName key="A002988">濟</persName>述《七<ptr target="fn07"/>宗論》，<persName key="A002989">宗</persName>著《經<lb ed="T" n="0373b08"/>目》及《數林》。</p>
	
	
